Package it.unicam.cs.massimopavoni.swarmsimulator.swarm.domain.parser

Interface StrategyParserHandler

public interface StrategyParserHandler
This interface is implemented to handle parsing of robot programs. Instances of this interface will be used as follows:
  1. at the beginning of the parsing method parsingStarted() parsingStarted()}
  2. each time the parser recognise a command, the corresponding method is invoked
  3. at the end of the parsing procedure method parsingDone() is invoked
